lead_paragraph: Bradley Dredge remains the man to beat after three rounds at the Made in Denmark event, but for once he had to settle for an over-par round at the Himmerland Golf & Spa Resort in Farso on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Under-Par Dredge Keeps Lead Despite Over-Par Round in Denmark
